# Day 97 – Sort Reports

**Estimated Time:** 1 hour

## Goal

Today you'll add a **Sort** feature so users can sort reports by:

* Patient Name (A → Z)
* Hemoglobin (Highest → Lowest)

This is a feature users expect in real applications.

